cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper presents a neural interactive-predictive system for tackling multimodal sequence to sequence tasks, specifically machine translation, image and video captioning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). However, given the focus on natural language generation and the use of neural models, cs.CL is the most likely sub-category. The other sub-categories are also relevant due to the multimodal nature of the tasks and the use of machine learning techniques.
